<normalizedToken originalValue="Brander’s">Brander's</normalizedToken>
specimen from Algiers (144.31, LINN). As a 
<typeStatus>syntype</typeStatus>
(which is not, by definition, the sole type of a name, unlike a 
<typeStatus>holotype</typeStatus>
, 
<typeStatus>lectotype</typeStatus>
or 
<typeStatus>neotype</typeStatus>
), 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Verdcourt’s">Verdcourt's</normalizedToken>
statement is not accepted as correctable to 
<typeStatus>lectotype</typeStatus>
under Art. 9.8.
</paragraph>
